    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Membranes stretched over the frames or shells of drums and sounded by being rubbed, plucked, or, most commonly, struck with the hands or beaters.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
